  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the beef pieces and cook until they are browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the tomato paste, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the beef broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 2 1/2 hours, or until the beef is tender.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
